# Cloudflare Pages headers.
#
# NB: COOP/COEP are deliberately NOT set. Cross-origin isolation would restore
# SharedArrayBuffer (used only by call e2e + the mic level meter), but COEP
# require-corp breaks the cross-origin iframes this app embeds — bot mini-apps
# (webApp.tsx / telegramWebView.ts) and payment provider frames (paymentCard.ts
# / paymentVerification.ts). The official web.telegram.org/k/ ships without it
# too, so we match that and keep mini-apps/payments working.

/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin

# Entry document must always revalidate so new deploys are picked up immediately
# (hashed JS/CSS chunks are content-addressed and cached by CF's defaults).
/
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/index.html
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
